@startuml
```plantuml
@startuml
!define DEVICONS https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tupadr3/plantuml-icon-font-sprites/master/devicons
!define AWS https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml/plantuml-aws/master/

package Client {
    node "Client Application" as client
}

node "Web Server\n(e.g., Nginx)" as webserver {
    [Nginx Configuration]
}

package "FastCGI Application" {
    component "ffunc Library\n(ffunc.c, ffunc.h)" as ffunc
    component "Application Logic\n(e.g., profile_service.c)" as applogic
    component "spdlog (Optional)" as spdlog
}

client --> webserver : Sends Request
webserver --> applogic : Forwards Request (FastCGI)
applogic ..> ffunc : Uses
applogic ..> spdlog : (Optional) Logging
applogic --> webserver : Sends Response (FastCGI)
webserver --> client : Sends Response

center footer Taymindis/fcgi-function

@enduml
```
@enduml